OL,4,C'sheer excitement' during unrest
OL,6,FA teenager who threw rocks at police
OL,7,Fout of "sheer excitement" during
OL,8,Fdisorder in Hartlepool has been put
OL,9,Fbehind bars.
OL,11,FLennox Crockett was caught throwing at
OL,12,Fleast four missiles during the hostile
OL,13,Fstand-off on Murray Street on 31 July.
OL,15,FTeesside Crown Court heard that the 19-
OL,16,Fyear-old also encouraged children to
OL,17,Ftake part as the violence erupted
OL,18,Facross the town.
