OL,3,CTeenager threw rocks at police out of
OL,4,C'sheer excitement' during unrest
OL,6,FOmar Ahmad, prosecuting, said Crockett
OL,7,Fwas initially recorded remonstrating
OL,8,Fwith the police before his behaviour
OL,9,Fbecame more aggressive.
OL,11,FHe said: "He is captured on footage,
OL,12,Fwith his hood up, throwing missiles at
OL,13,Fthe police line.
OL,15,F"He is seen picking a rock from the
OL,16,Fground and throwing at the police
OL,17,Fline. I count on the footage that he
OL,18,Fthrew rocks at least four times.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
