OL,3,CTeenager threw rocks at police out of
OL,4,C'sheer excitement' during unrest
OL,6,F"He was often at the front of the
OL,7,Fcrowd alongside small children and at
OL,8,Fone point is encouraging others,
OL,9,Fincluding the children, to push
OL,10,Fforward at the police."
OL,12,FCrockett, of Denham Green,
OL,13,FMiddlesbrough, pleaded guilty to
OL,14,Fviolent disorder in Hartlepool on 31
OL,15,FJuly and possession of cocaine,
OL,16,Fcannabis and nitrous oxide which was
OL,17,Fseized from his address when he was
OL,18,Farrested on 14 July.
