OL,3,CTeenager threw rocks at police out of
OL,4,C'sheer excitement' during unrest
OL,6,FMichele Turner, mitigating, said her
OL,7,Fclient got involved with the disorder
OL,8,Fand threw rocks out of "sheer
OL,9,Fexcitement" and was protesting about
OL,10,Fthe police and not any other sector of
OL,11,Fsociety.
OL,13,FShe said: "This is a young man who has
OL,14,Fbeen trying to fit in since early
OL,15,Fchildhood.
OL,17,F"He struggled to make friends and
OL,18,Fstruggled in the education system.
