OL,6,F"He learned that if he acted the fool,
OL,7,Fhe got laughs, he got recognition from
OL,8,Fpeers in an effort to fit in."
OL,10,FOn Monday 16 September, Judge Francis
OL,11,FLaird KC sentenced Crockett to 18
OL,12,Fmonths in a young offenders' institute
OL,13,Ffollowing his guilty pleas.
OL,15,F"I recognise that you struggled with
OL,16,Fschool and you lack many of the tools
OL,17,Fneeded to forge an independent life,"
OL,18,Fthe judge said.
